                "invention-title": [
                    "Resource recycling method for overhaul slag",
                    "一种大修渣资源化回收利用的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a method for recycling overhaul slag, which comprises the following steps of: reacting the overhaul slag with a certain amount of calcium chloride and a small amount of hydrogen peroxide under a pressurizing condition, so that lithium element in the overhaul slag enters a solution, and soluble fluorine ions are combined with calcium ions to generate a calcium fluoride product; then, leaching residues are subjected to step-by-step flotation separation, carbon concentrate, calcium fluoride and cryolite products are obtained in sequence, and an aqueous solution is circulated to the flotation technological process; and performing impurity removal, concentration and hydrothermal treatment on the leachate to prepare a high-value lithium carbonate product. According to the method, multiple valuable substances in the overhaul slag are recycled in a low-energy-consumption and high-valued mode, and resource recycling of the overhaul slag is achieved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种大修渣资源化回收利用的方法，该方法是将大修渣与一定量的氯化钙和少量的过氧化氢在加压条件下反应，使得大修渣中的锂元素进入到溶液中，可溶氟离子与钙离子结合生成氟化钙产品，然后浸出渣通过分步浮选分离依次得到碳精矿、氟化钙和冰晶石产品，水溶液循环到浮选工艺流程；浸出液通过除杂、浓缩、水热制备成高值碳酸锂产品。该方法低能耗、高值化分别回收大修渣中多种有价物质，实现大修渣的资源化回收利用。"
                }
            ]
